sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor A as Alice
    participant GW as WS Gateway
    participant PS as Presence Svc
    participant MQ as Message Bus
    actor B as Bob

    A->>+GW: WS connect (JWT)
    GW->>+PS: register(Alice)
    PS--)MQ: presence.online(Alice)
    PS-->>-GW: session ok
    GW-->>-A: connected

    Note over A,B: Bob joins mid-conversation

    create participant W as Worker
    GW->>W: spawn typing-indicator worker

    loop While typing
        A-)GW: typing=true
        GW--)B: peer typing…
    end

    A->>+GW: sendMessage("hi Bob")
    GW--)MQ: publish(msg)
    MQ--)B: deliver(msg)
    B-->>-GW: ack(msgId)

    A<<->>B: end-to-end key exchange

    destroy W
    GW-xW: stop worker

    B->>+GW: WS disconnect
    GW->>PS: unregister(Bob)
    PS--)MQ: presence.offline(Bob)
    GW-->>-B: bye
